description: Namaskaar Dosto, is video mein maine aapse baat ki hai Apple ke latest iPhone 12 family ke baare mein jaha pe hai latest iPhone 12, iPhone 12 Mini, iPhone 12 Pro aur iPhone 12 Pro Max. Aur yaha maine share ki hai aapke saath iPhone 12 Pro Smartphone ki unboxing aur ek first look, jaha pe kaafi interesting improvements hai is iPhone 12 Pro mein jaha baat hai 6.1 Super Retina XDR OLED Display ki, saath mein Apple A14 Bionic chip hai aur fir hai ek triple rear camera system jaha hai 12MP Normal + 12MP Ultra wide + 12MP 2x zoom ke saath jiske saath LIDAR bhi available hai. Saath mein front camera bhi hai 12MP ka aur aap sabhi cameras se 4K 60fps mein videos bana sakte hai aur Dolby Vision HDR mein videos record kar sakte hai.
